casebody.data:
Luis LA-CASSE, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2350, 3D17-2410 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 20, 2017 SUAREZ, LAGOA and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that the above referenced proceedings are hereby consolidated for all appellate purposes under case no. 3D17-2350.

Following review of the petition for writ of certiorari under case no. 3D17-2350, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.

The appeal under case no. 3D17-2410 shall be treated as a petition for writ of prohibition, and it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
